createdStartDate.description: Obtains order returns created after this date (inclusively), in ISO 8601 format.

pageToken.description: The token returned by the previous request.

maxResults.description: The maximum number of order returns to return in the response, used for paging. The default value is 25 returns per page, and the maximum allowed value is 250 returns per page.

createdEndDate.description: Obtains order returns created before this date (inclusively), in ISO 8601 format.

orderBy.description: Return the results in the specified order.
